data.description: Super cute ranch located on almost half an acre that backs up to a beautiful horse farm. Great location! Just minutes to I-75 and Genesys hospital. 3 bedroom two on the main level one in the lower level, hardwood floors, coved ceilings, large 3 seasons room, partially finished basement, large garage attached with a breezeway and storage room, extra storage shed, central air and more! Hurry! Schedule a showing today!
